License: MIT License
Description: 
        django-blastplus
        ================
        
        A simple Django app to conduct web-based homology search with blast+.
        
        
        Requirements
        ------------
        
        1. Blast+
        2. Python 2.7
        3. Django 1.10
        
        ::
        
            pip install django
        
        4. Biopython
        
        ::
        
            pip install biopython
        
        
